    <j.0:comment xml:lang="fr">Parliament adopted 6 amendments. While the Commission could appreciate the spirit of all the amendments, four of them had to be rejected for practical considerations. Cette proposition a été modifiée suite à l'avis du PE du 28/05/1998.</j.0:comment>
